race.description: Sportsbet Country Mile Series Ht-Nutrien Ag Hcp
race.comment: BIG SUE (6) looks well placed back to 1400m and back to provincial grade. He will likely concede a start to some of those rivals with a bit more toe but he will be strong late. Happy to back him each-way. DUBAI DANCER (4) lead, controlled and won well last time. He's drawn well with the claim again so he will give himself every chance of making it back-to-back wins. COME ALONG JEFFREY (1) might be ready to run a big race now. He was better last start and he's drawn low to hold the rail. He might make DUBAI DANCER work to cross. MISO (3) has to be rated a top three chance again given his recent form, while ALCOSHARE (5) is another worth some thought for wider plays.
